<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an N. von Taufkirchen zu Guttenburg</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Herausgabe des Zehnts zu Mörmossen, den Kathrin Lautenmacher, Bürgerin zu Nürnberg, von ihrem Vater geerbt hat.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_194" id="96v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_194_r2l11">Dem ~ Tauffkırcher cʒu <expan>Gutemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> geſeſſen </ab>
</div>
