<ab facs="#facs_194_r2l22">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>eingenome<ex>n</ex></expan></del> habt / vnd ew nü darüber <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒehenden ſelber </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_194_r2l24">cʒevntervvinden / vnd ſie 
